<%- 
  title "NFTs"
  description "NFTs owned by Josh Pigford"
-%>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
  <h1>NFTs</h1>
  <p>I dove down the NFT rabbit hole starting in early 2021. Here's my collection across both ETH and XTZ!</p>

  <div class="not-prose">
  <ul role="list" class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-8 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-x-6 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-x-8">
    <% @nfts.each do |nft| %>
    <li class="relative">
      <%= link_to nft_path(nft.slug) do %>
      <div class="block w-full overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-lg group aspect-w-1 aspect-h-1 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-offset-2 focus-within:ring-offset-gray-100 focus-within:ring-indigo-500">
        <%= image_tag nft_image(nft.asset_image_url), class: 'object-cover pointer-events-none group-hover:opacity-75' %>
      </div>
      <p class="block mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 truncate pointer-events-none"><%= nft.asset_name %></p>
      <p class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 pointer-events-none"><%= nft.collection_name %></p>
      <% end %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>